# Vertical Registry Refactor Plan

## Context

The app currently supports 3 hardcoded categories (`pharmacy`, `fuel_station`, `mobile_money`). Adding the 11 new verticals from the Kasi Insight meeting notes requires touching ~15 files with ~85+ references. This refactor creates a single source of truth so adding a new vertical means editing one config object and running one DB migration.

## New Verticals to Add

`alcohol_outlet`, `retail_kiosk`, `billboard`, `fmcg`, `transport_station_hub`, `census_satellite_groundtruth`, `fuel_fleet`, `ngo_services`, `public_goods`, `competitor_intelligence`, `water_point`

