## Phase 4: Database migration

**File: `supabase/migrations/YYYYMMDD_add_verticals.sql`** (NEW)
- Drop old CHECK constraint, add new one with all vertical IDs:
  ```sql
  ALTER TABLE point_events DROP CONSTRAINT IF EXISTS point_events_category_check;
  ALTER TABLE point_events ADD CONSTRAINT point_events_category_check
    CHECK (category IN ('pharmacy','fuel_station','mobile_money','alcohol_outlet','retail_kiosk','billboard','fmcg','transport_station_hub','census_satellite_groundtruth','fuel_fleet','ngo_services','public_goods','competitor_intelligence','water_point'));
  ```

